decision 1/104 of 30 June 2006. 
</p>
<p>28. During the ensuing discussion, at the same meeting, and at the 10th meeting on the same 
date, the following made statements: 
</p>
<p> (<i>a</i>) Representatives of States members of the Council:  Algeria (on behalf of the 
