<p><b>3.  Methods of work and agenda 
</b></p>
<p>36. At the 3rd and 4th meetings, on 30 November 2006, the Council discussed its methods of 
work and agenda, including its rules of procedure. 
</p>
<p>37. During the ensuing discussion, at the same meetings, the following made statements: 
</p>
