<p> (<i>b</i>) After the fourth preambular paragraph, he inserted a new fifth preambular 
paragraph to read as follows:  &#8220;Recognizing the efforts already made for the webcast of its 
sessions&#8221;; 
</p>
<p> (<i>c</i>) In paragraph 2, subparagraph (a), he deleted the last word &#8220;and&#8221;; 
</p>
<p> (<i>d</i>) In paragraph 2, after subparagraph (a) he inserted two new subparagraphs (b) 
and (c), to read as follows:   
</p>
<p>&#8220;(b) webcast for all the sessions of the Human Rights Council&#8221;;  
</p>
<p> &#8220;(c) documentation in all official United Nations languages in a timely 
manner&#8221;;   
</p>
<p>(<i>e</i>) He renumbered subsequently former subparagraph (b) as subparagraph (d);  
</p>
<p>(<i>f</i>) In paragraph 2, new subparagraph (d) he deleted the word &#8220;mechanism&#8221;. 
